guest_stars.name: Dan Musgrove

episodes.name: Grid Connection
episodes.overview: In an epic battle, the Beast Morphers team up with the Dino Thunder, Dino Charge, and Mighty Morphin Power Rangers to defeat the newest member of Evox's team.

episodes.name: Golden Opportunity
episodes.overview: Nate is reunited with his do-gooder parents, who offer him a compelling and difficult choice.

episodes.name: Goin' Ape
episodes.overview: Ravi and Roxy's anniversary hits a major snag when a misunderstanding gets out of control.

episodes.name: The Silva Switch
episodes.overview: Nate and Steel accidentally swap bodies!

episodes.name: Fossil Frenzy
episodes.overview: When Zoey accidentally ruins her brother's chances for a scholarship, she’ll do anything to make it right.

episodes.name: Crunch Time
episodes.overview: Devon falls victim to a bad influence, which affects his relationship with Cruise.

episodes.name: Source Code
episodes.overview: Nate makes a horrifying discovery and must rely on the wisdom of an ally to help him work through it.

episodes.name: Evox Unleashed
episodes.overview: Evox finally executes his master plan, and the Rangers must do everything they can to stop him, even potentially sacrifice one of their own.

27.name: Beast Morphers (2)
27.overview: As Evox builds his army to overtake Earth, the Rangers must stop him with new zords, enhanced abilities and unexpected allies.

episodes.name: Destination Dinohenge
episodes.overview: Reporter Amelia accompanies Ollie and his mom, Dr. Akana, to investigate the mysterious Dinohenge statues; the trio run into an evil warrior named Void Knight and a threat that puts the entire world in danger.

episodes.name: Sporix Unleashed
episodes.overview: Ollie carries out a plan to catch Sporix without his teammates' knowledge; Ollie realizes the benefit of working as a team.

episodes.name: Lost Signal
episodes.overview: The Rangers intercept a mysterious message from outer space and Zayto is desperate to know if it was sent from his home planet; unable to decipher the message and losing hope, Zayto remembers another important message from the past.

episodes.name: New Recruits
episodes.overview: General Boomtower tries to steal a mysterious orb from the city museum; when the Rangers struggle to stop him, they get help from an unexpected source.

episodes.name: Winning Attitude
episodes.overview: Izzy is determined to win a big race with the help of her Special Olympics athlete cousin, Lily; after Lily misses a training session and Izzy rejects more help, her sportsmanship is put to the test.

episodes.name: Superstition Strikes
episodes.overview: Amelia thinks she's cursed with bad luck and is reluctant to help the Rangers, afraid she'll cause more harm; Amelia learns the truth about luck when monsters attack the base.

episodes.name: Stego Search
episodes.overview: The Warden takes away Javi's keytar, putting him in a bad mood, which he refuses to explain to the team. Javi is forced to open up about his problems in order to find his Zord.

episodes.name: Unexpected Guest
episodes.overview: A familiar face arrives on Earth and Zayto dismisses his quest as a distraction; after he saves the Rangers from a powerful Sporix Beast, Zayto realizes an important lesson.

episodes.name: Cut Off
episodes.overview: The Rangers tease Ollie for bringing all of his gadgets on a camping trip. But his tech might be their only hope when sinister Sporix suddenly attack.

episodes.name: Phoning Home
episodes.overview: A knight from Zayto's home planet suddenly appears at Dinohedge with a message that might be too good to be true... and Solon has her suspicions.

episodes.name: McScary Manor
episodes.overview: Amelia hunts for ghosts at a creepy mansion. But there's no supernatural sighting -- only a fierce face-off with pyramid-shaped Tombtress.

episodes.name: Super Hotshot
episodes.overview: Izzy is convinced a new coach is going to take her athletics to the next level. However, her training aspirations are put to the test when she discovers the coach's true motivations

episodes.name: The Matchmaker
episodes.overview: Javi thinks Izzy has a crush on a friend and he sets them up on a date, but his assumption causes big problems when the monsters smell love in the air.

episodes.name: Old Foes
episodes.overview: Ollie boasts to his friends that he's afraid of nothing. But when the other Dino Fury Rangers are captured by a formidable foe, Ollie realizes his biggest fear.

episodes.name: Storm Surge
episodes.overview: Ollie agrees to help Javi with a story, but his desire for new tech distracts him from his promise. The villains exploit his obsession, and Ollie learns a lesson about priorities.

episodes.name: Ancient History
episodes.overview: Aiyon, the new Gold Ranger, reveals the dark truth about Zayto's past and the Dino Fury Rangers learn what makes a true leader.

episodes.name: Our Hero
episodes.overview: Getting a free ice cream for a heroic act goes to Aiyon's head. But later on, when his Zord is captured, he learns what it means to be a true hero.

episodes.name: Crossed Wires
episodes.overview: Izzy attempts to hide her struggles in electronics class put the Rangers at risk when they need those skills during a battle.

episodes.name: The Makeover
episodes.overview: The villains use a Sporix Beast with body-swapping powers to chase pirate treasure, interrupting Amelia's attempts to make over Pop-Pop for a date.

episodes.name: Waking Nightmares
episodes.overview: Zayto is trapped on a distant planet seeking new Zords, and Aiyon makes a risky trip to save him. Together, they confront the nightmares of their past.

episodes.name: Void Trap
episodes.overview: The Rangers need Dr. Akana's help to stop Void Knight's evil scheme. But Ollie disagrees with Zayto's plan, afraid it will put his mother in danger.

episodes.name: Secret Santa
episodes.overview: While the Rangers fight to get Santa's magic sketchbook back from the villains, Javi and Solon are caught in a trap. Will they escape?

28.name: Dino Fury (1)
28.overview: When an army of powerful alien beings is unleashed on Earth threatening life as we know it, a brand-new team of Power Rangers, fueled by the pre-historic power of the dinosaurs, are recruited to deal with the threat.

episodes.name: Numero Uno
episodes.overview: Void Knight suddenly returns, and a new member of his vicious crew joins Slyther and Mucus in tricking the Rangers and stealing a valuable Dino Key.

episodes.name: The Festival
episodes.overview: The Rangers must divide their fighting duties when Slyther and pirate robot Wreckmate challenge each other to see who can be more destructive.

episodes.name: Missing Pieces
episodes.overview: Solon's system gets an update. Javi, Izzy and the Rangers spot a Sporix beast — but not before evil Occulo tries to nab it first.

episodes.name: Tiny Trouble
episodes.overview: Aiyon reconnects with a shrunken Zord, but Occulo and Wreckmate try chasing it down for Void Knight's secret plans.

episodes.name: Stitched Up
episodes.overview: Izzy gets frustrated about the outfit her mom designed for the prom.  The Rangers battle a Sporix creature with an appetite for trash.

episodes.name: Jam Session
episodes.overview: Javi notices a powerful Dino Key on a band leader’s necklace. The Rangers power up to face off against Void Knight’s nasty new gizmo.

episodes.name: New Leaf
episodes.overview: Santaura convinces Void Knight and wicked Squashblight to contaminate the city’s water supply and turn all the residents into trees.

episodes.name: Serious Business
episodes.overview: The Rangers question Void Knight’s intentions. Santaura comes up with a new strategy to hunt down her former partner in crime.

episodes.name: The Hunt
episodes.overview: Amelia leads the crew on a search for a ghost caught on camera. A new robot programmed to crush and conquer hunts down the Rangers.

episodes.name: Losers Weapers
episodes.overview: Aiyon and Izzy find a secret stash of cash — and a powerful necklace that turns creatures mega-sized.

episodes.name: The Copycat
episodes.overview: Javi must come up with a new tune after his song for a competition is stolen. Mucus suggests a fresh way to beat the Rangers.

episodes.name: Ultimate Mystery
episodes.overview: When Jane vetoes a Buzzblast story on bigfoot, Amelia tells Stan and Annie to bend the rules and publish it anyway, but when her colleagues end up in danger, Amelia learns an important lesson about responsibility.

episodes.name: Love Hate
episodes.overview: Ollie tries to ask Amelia out, but a miscommunication leads to Amelia thinking he doesn't like her.

episodes.name: Rafkon Revealed
episodes.overview: The Ranger teens head to Rafkon to stop Lord Zedd, but because of a prophecy, Aiyon takes unnecessary risks.

episodes.name: Morphin Master
episodes.overview: The other Morphin Masters are angry to discover the Green Morphin Master has broken their vow to never intervene in mortal affairs. But when the Rangers and the Green Morphin Master work together, the Morphin Masters have a change of heart.

episodes.name: Wishful Thinking
episodes.overview: When a monster's meddling gives Javi a big break, he must come to terms with the fact that the key to success is hard work.

episodes.name: Things Unspoken
episodes.overview: Fern is offered a place at an elite sports college; Fern and Izzy's relationship is put to three test.

episodes.name: Guilt Trip
episodes.overview: Izzy is torn following Fern's acceptance to a faraway college. The Rangers try to stop Quickspine and Mucus from stealing Carlos' key.

episodes.name: Bad Vibes
episodes.overview: When Izzy and Javi are hit by blasts from a special weapon, they're brainwashed into helping the Void Queen with her plot to steal the Sporix.

episodes.name: The Invasion
episodes.overview: A band of Rafkonians arrive looking to colonize Earth, but the Rangers talk them into joining forces to stop the Void Queen's Sporix beasts.

episodes.name: The Truth
episodes.overview: As citizens flee in the wake of the Sporix beast invasion, the Rangers find an energy cocoon created by the Void Queen that could destroy Pine Ridge.

episodes.name: The Nemesis
episodes.overview: After Tarrick moves the energy cocoon outside of the city, the Rangers must do battle with the Void Queen and her massive Nemesis beast.

29.name: Dino Fury (2)
29.overview: The Power Rangers band together with mighty new Dino Keys to stop more squads of Sporix beasts — and revived enemies out for revenge.

episodes.name: Lightning Strikes
episodes.overview: Bajillia enlists Lord Zedd to lead her armies in an intergalactic war — and things only get worse when the two capture a Power Ranger for their team.

episodes.name: Beyond Repair
episodes.overview: Team Cosmic Fury prepares for a possible invasion from Lord Zedd while Amelia tries to cure an evilized Ranger and Javi learns to accept his new loss.

episodes.name: Off Grid
episodes.overview: Stranded on a faraway planet with no powers, Team Cosmic Fury scrambles to figure out a way home while Earth suffers an invasion from enemy forces.

episodes.name: Team Work
episodes.overview: Ollie races Team Cosmic Fury to find Zayto, but the Zenith Ranger's location is anyone's guess. They'd better move fast though: Lord Zedd's forces loom!

episodes.name: Rock Out
episodes.overview: When Bajillia discovers a long-lost Zord on a mining planet, the Rangers must create a musical distraction to stop her from using it as a war weapon.

episodes.name: Take Off
episodes.overview: Solon goes missing right as the Rangers prepare to fly the base back to Earth. But the team has bigger problems: Ollie's tracker has led him to Erridus.

episodes.name: Operation Seasoning
episodes.overview: To save Pine Ridge, Team Cosmic Fury must dismantle the system of Squidrills creating an anti-Zord forcefield around Earth — with the help of a spy.

episodes.name: Switching Sides
episodes.overview: Two ex-villains should be the last people to cure Ollie, but Aiyon has a plan that just might work. Meanwhile, Zayto's secret becomes harder to hide.

episodes.name: Master Plan
episodes.overview: The connection to the Morphin Grid is in danger, unless the team can travel to Eltar and take back the Master Captivator and Ollie — without backup.

episodes.name: The End
episodes.overview: If Team Cosmic Fury can't stabilize the Master Captivator, a wave of pure evil threatens to wipe out all the good in the universe. No pressure, right?

30.name: Cosmic Fury
30.overview: When Lord Zedd returns more powerful than ever, Team Cosmic Fury takes to the cosmos to battle the emperor of evil — and save the universe as we know it.
